:::

::: {.absolute top=245 right=230 style="color: red;"}
r
:::

:::

::: incremental
* $A_{circle} = \pi r^2$
* $A_{square} = 4 \times r^2$
* $\displaystyle \pi = \frac{4 \times A_{circle}}{A_{square}} \approx \frac{4 \times \text{darts in circle}}{\text{total darts}}$
:::



